possible and general guidelines are available in shastras, but we ca=\r\nn&#39;t be certain about the specific impact of each action. One thing is for s=\r\nure - remedial measure for overcoming a karma has to be commensurate with t=\r\nhe karma\n itself.&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;You need only small force to push a cat out =\r\nof your way, but need a large force to push an elephant.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;c=\r\nolor:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13px;font-family:arial, helvetica, clean, sans-=\r\nserif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Best regar=\r\nds,&lt;br&gt;Narasimha&lt;br&gt;--------&lt;br&gt;Astrology &amp; Spirituality Resources: &lt;a =\r\nrel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot; href=3D&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot;=\r\n&gt;http://www.VedicAstrologer.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);f=\r\nont-size:13px;font-family:arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif;background-co=\r\nlor:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;--------&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;blockquot=\r\ne style=3D&quot;border-left:2px solid rgb(16, 16, 255);margin-left:5px;margin-to=\r\np:5px;padding-left:5px;&quot;&gt;  &lt;div style=3D&quot;font-family:arial, helvetica, sans=\r\n-serif;font-size:10pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;div style=3D&quot;font-family:times new roman, new yor=\r\nk, times, serif;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;div dir=3D&quot;ltr&quot;&gt; &lt;font face=3D&quot;Arial&quot; si=\r\nze=3D&quot;2&quot;&gt;\n &lt;hr size=3D&quot;1&quot;&gt;  &lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;From:&lt;/spa=\r\nn&gt;&lt;/b&gt; Ajit Krishnan &lt;ajit.krishnan@...&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;=\r\nfont-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;To:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; vedic-wisdom@yahoogroups.com &lt;br&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;spa=\r\nn style=3D&quot;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;Sent:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; Tuesday, February 26, 2013 1=\r\n1:29 PM&lt;br&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&qu